> If even one of those goroutines does not have a defer set up, then an exception can crash the program.<p>This might help.<p><pre><code>    func GoCatch(f func ()) {
      go func () {
        defer func () {
          e := recover()
          if e != nil {
            log.Stderr(e.String())
          }
        }()
        f()
      }
    }</code></pre>
